Emaar Seeks $800 Million Loan Backed by Dubai Mall, Reuters Says

-- B y   S h a j i   M a t h e w
-- 
2011-09-29T14:29:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/emaar-seeks-800-million-loan-backed-by-dubai-mall-reuters-says.html
Emaar Properties PJSC (EMAAR)  is seeking to
raise $800 million in loans, using four of its shopping malls
including the Dubai Mall as collateral, Reuters reported, citing
unidentified people.  The facility, which consists of a five-year tranche and an
eight-year amortising loan, is being arranged by Dubai Islamic
Bank, National Bank of  Abu Dhabi  and Standard Chartered Plc, the
news agency reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  